Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.24,0:01:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏龙知道风早在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.27,0:01:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才跟他聊了会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.86,0:01:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的啥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.57,0:01:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.48,0:01:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 那算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.99,0:01:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得 多数情况都没得到别人理解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.70,0:01:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多数情况都没能说出心里话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.44,0:01:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使那样 我还是喜欢那个努力的黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.63,0:01:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.82,0:02:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想传达给他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.14,0:02:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要传达到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.78,0:02:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要传达到
