Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.78,0:03:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颤抖不止
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.51,0:03:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向风早同学诉说心意的时候到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.96,0:04:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.28,0:04:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你弄哭了 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.86,0:04:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你那么的困扰 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只顾着自说自话 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.93,0:04:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有什么要向我说的话 就说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.02,0:04:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是什么 我都想听
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.11,0:04:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心意不会变
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.50,0:04:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的喜欢跟黑沼的喜欢不一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.44,0:04:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要找吉田和矢野的话 应该在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.53,0:04:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我是来见风早同学的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.84,0:05:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来找风早同学说清楚的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.15,0:05:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.54,0:05:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好 就这样好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.98,0:05:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风早同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.15,0:05:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来 我不管做什么 别人总会向我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 第一次遇到风早同学的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:06:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到你笑着对我说的那声「谢谢」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.44,0:06:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的非常高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从来没想过要一视同仁地对待你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.07,0:06:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 我还是很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.26,0:06:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命仿佛突然上了色彩一般
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.10,0:06:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风早同学改变了我的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.28,0:06:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的一个存在每天都在改变着我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我却做出了跟那时候的风早同学完全相反的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 这次不是来道歉 而是要跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.08,0:07:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你对我微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你和我攀谈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你对我那么亲切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.50,0:07:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你让我体验了以前从未体验过的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.34,0:07:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.24,0:07:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.34,0:07:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.60,0:07:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.05,0:07:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.88,0:08:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.26,0:08:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在难以传达出去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.99,0:08:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道应该如何用语言完整地表达这份感情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.58,0:08:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只知道说「喜欢」　我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.21,0:08:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 别拉开 我现在...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.23,0:08:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他看到我现在的表情的话 会很不好意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.54,0:09:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子能顺利说出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.45,0:09:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.72,0:09:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风早
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 风早 在的话举个手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会出事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.36,0:09:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有龙在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.76,0:09:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙 风早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.64,0:09:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.58,0:10:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风早
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,0:10:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上他是不会撒谎的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.46,0:10:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是问你风早在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.36,0:10:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 对方是笨蛋丈 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你们有看到黑沼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.10,0:10:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没...没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 你们真没用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.00,0:10:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事 要带话的话我们可以帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.84,0:10:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不能让你们知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.66,0:10:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想到一个好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.66,0:10:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有戏了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.87,0:10:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定不会有好事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.13,0:10:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我去教室那边看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.46,0:10:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 她回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.17,0:10:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那刚才怎么不说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.51,0:10:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.77,0:10:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在又想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.93,0:10:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.82,0:10:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 教室
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.55,0:10:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑...黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.37,0:12:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我...我...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.58,0:12:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别 别躲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.23,0:12:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉我一直都没有认真地从正面去看黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.55,0:13:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 风早
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.84,0:13:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 贞子？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.91,0:13:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿痞在找你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.28,0:13:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什么重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来 在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.13,0:13:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们做什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.71,0:13:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.81,0:13:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.31,0:13:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老...老师找我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:13:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.72,0:13:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风早
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.63,0:13:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在搞什么啊 找你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.51,0:14:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.09,0:14:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.31,0:14:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事情无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待会聚在一起时吃的零食 咸甜七三分可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.37,0:14:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是八二？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你去！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.57,0:14:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 失败了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.00,0:14:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个 要是出错的话就要在男生的衣服上出哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.85,0:14:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 就在丈的那身上做吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.85,0:15:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 告白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.78,0:15:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.74,0:15:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「算是」是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.57,0:15:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心里想的连十分之一都没传达给他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.68,0:15:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 风早有什么反应
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.46,0:15:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反应...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.71,0:15:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎...怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶...诶...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好好干活吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.83,0:15:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那...那是我们要说的话！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.38,0:15:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还跑到这里干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这班主任很为班级着想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于明天的表演 有事情要找黑沼商量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘...忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.98,0:15:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事情明天说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.80,0:15:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈也是 干嘛让他进来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.44,0:15:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想到一个好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.73,0:15:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那肯定会给裁判留下好印象的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.22,0:16:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑沼 来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.90,0:16:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是...是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 那袋子不是给我们的慰劳品吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.23,0:16:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定又跟谁打赌了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.22,0:16:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看他那一脸别有用心的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.74,0:16:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别...别有用心！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.54,0:16:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样的 明天的化装游行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.24,0:16:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单人表演的时候 拿这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.35,0:16:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.20,0:16:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也没法本着纯洁之心去正视风早同学了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.63,0:16:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺...挺好的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.54,0:16:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.91,0:16:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他都对我说「心意不会变的」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我都不知道该怎么办了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.69,0:16:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再给我一次机会的话...如果还有机会的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.27,0:17:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问你 你觉得翔太或者其他人就没有私心了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.78,0:17:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是这里产生的 有是正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.42,0:17:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 明天把这些东西放到评委们的碟子里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.39,0:17:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每人一个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.77,0:17:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗 有私心是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.98,0:17:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.83,0:17:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 你刚才说的那些 明天对他本人再说一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磨叽磨叽的太烦了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.99,0:17:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.73,0:17:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.00,0:18:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才是不是进行了一段很精彩的演说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.39,0:18:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上去找翔太
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那边的颜料够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.25,0:18:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会赶不及
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.61,0:18:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会赶不及
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.45,0:18:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通宵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.93,0:18:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿痞到女生那边了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田家？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.95,0:18:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们小心阿痞来袭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.44,0:18:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是小心 是应该警戒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.07,0:18:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.41,0:18:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来没必要特意跑过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.39,0:18:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.05,0:18:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我上个厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.61,0:19:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 风早「唯有私心」太君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.68,0:19:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.91,0:19:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.60,0:19:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私心也是心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.78,0:19:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.11,0:19:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.74,0:19:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们听好了 翔太的脑子里就只有私心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.81,0:19:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是阿痞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.30,0:19:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}够了 你给我滚！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.41,0:19:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿痞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.52,0:19:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风早？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私心？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.37,0:19:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 翔太 我可是特意告诉你一个好消息的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.91,0:19:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两眼放光感激涕零吧 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.86,0:19:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能赶得及吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的 可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.34,0:19:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 阿痞也到男生那边了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.19,0:19:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.24,0:19:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在屋外吵闹什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.18,0:20:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸亏他早早就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.46,0:20:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心跳不止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.79,0:20:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子 明天什么时候跟他说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.11,0:20:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢欣期待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.47,0:20:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}打算是在游行之前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.99,0:20:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.50,0:20:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐立不安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.36,0:20:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有多久没有如此期待第二天的到来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.65,0:20:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风早 私心是说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.89,0:20:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒想问
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.53,0:20:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 被痞缠上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.53,0:20:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈只知道吃零食
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.77,0:20:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 龙要睡到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.43,0:20:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\an8\c&H979785&\bord0}明天再好好谈一次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.71,0:20:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想快点...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.51,0:21:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想快点...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.22,0:21:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想快点...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.84,0:21:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到TA
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=======预告=======
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.12,0:22:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二人同心 定能...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.18,0:22:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二人同行 更能...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.38,0:22:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一回 从今开始
